title: Photo: Yuvraj Singh's Wife Hazel Keech Is What Every Girlfriend Is Like On Valentines Day | MissMalini
text:
Divya Rao Feb . 15 . 2017 Yuvraj Singh and Hazel Keech 
Yuvraj Singh and Hazel Keech tied the knot last year in a big, fat Indian wedding . The two looked absolutely gorgeous and so much in love! They often post super cute pictures of themselves and they did the same this Valentines Day too. Yuvi shared this hilariously cute photo of Hazel and him, and this will remind you of every girlfriend on this planet! Take a look. A post shared by Yuvraj Singh (@yuvisofficial) on Feb 13, 2017 at 11:55pm PST 
Hahaha LOVE it!
